# Client component placement

Canonical: `PROJECT_RULES.md` § component placement

## Three tiers

| Tier | Path | Ex |
|------|------|-----|
| Primitives | `@eden-ecommerce/common/fields/*` | Input, Label, Select |
| Generic composition | `components/{domain}/` | `forms/`: FormField, MultiStepForm; `search/`: SearchBox, filters; `panels/`: PanelRenderer |
| Route biz | `app/{route}/_components/` | providers, sections, submit wiring for that route |

## Traps

* `components/{domain}/` — reusable composition for that domain; props-in like common. No route wiring, domain Zod, or API hooks.
* `components/forms/` — Formik wrappers/hooks only. No domain schemas or route sections.
* `app/{route}/_components/` — route providers, sections, submit. Compose from `@components/{domain}/*` + `@components/fields/*`.
* Zod/API types shared by UI + `app/api/*`/hooks → `lib/` — not `_components/`.
* Route-only UI (sandbox hub, integration debug, onboarding demo) → `app/sandbox/_components/` — generic search/forms live in `components/{domain}/`.
